						<p>This inscription is damaged and incomplete.</p>						

						<p>It records that a certain Mattayaṉ, son of Kāṇaya Bōyaṇḍaṉ received 25 coins from the <hi rend="italic">Paṇḍāram</hi> and gave in lieu of its yield, 3 <hi rend="italic">māḍai.</hi></p>						

